// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-3068 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: a2a588b1-0770-5fc5-accc-7f01059afda0

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:10*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:7*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:8*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:9*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:18.04-ESM*")
